title: Prevents asynchronous conflicts in fragments
message:
Prevents asynchronous conflicts in fragments

Even async callbacks are run on main thread, fragments may have been
detached from activity and a new instance is used.
Then, you should test if fragment is still active before running any
operation, especially UI actions that will raise an exception.
